node.text:
THE VERTICAL DIET hard copy will be in Barnes & Noble Aug 10th and is now available for pre-order on Amazon. 
.
Co-authored by Damon McCune PhD, RDN, LD @drdamonmccune 
.
Damon and I have received over 100,000 DM’s, emails and messages from vertical diet users all over the world with Questions, comments, Kudo’s and yes, even some complaints, which we’ve used to continue to expand upon and update The Vertical Diet to help as many people as possible achieve their health and fitness goals. 
.
Victory Belt Publishing has done an outstanding job with the quality of this book and we’re excited to share it with you!!
.
Please be sure to let us know what you think. Thank you!!

.

When the Big Dog’s away, the cats will play!
.
2 sets of 500 yard 100lb sled drags. 
.
Damn, The air is thin here in Albuquerque 😓
.
@beattrainer 
@mr_nfp

node.text:
#Repost @kyle_cavnar with @make_repost
・・・
“The best diet is the one you’ll follow”. Excited to dive into this amazingly well put together hard copy of @theverticaldiet …just browsing through it and holy sh*t; my college text books were not this well written or in depth. Congrats to author and my new friend @drdamonmccune and all his hard work and research that went into this. To put the depth of credible information into perspective, the last 23 pages are just of citations from studies this diet is based off of 😬 (Est. over 500 studies!)

Another one bites the dust!
.
Less than 3,000 leg days left before I’m my pops age (he’s 90). 
.
I’ll be working on these elevator squats for a while. 
.
Went back to the @officialflexwheeler style quad workouts from 2009. 
.
Single leg extensions (mind muscle)
Leg press < 2 min rests (high intensity)
Substituted elevator squats for hack squats
Finish with banded step ups or lunges. 
.
The backside of the mountain may not be as glamorous but it’s a peaceful place ☮️
.

👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇👇

.

.

THE VERTICAL DIET hard copy will be in Barnes & Noble Aug 10th and is now available for pre-order on Amazon. 
.
Co-authored by Damon McCune PhD, RDN, LD @drdamonmccune 
.
Damon and I have received over 100,000 DM’s, emails and messages from vertical diet users all over the world with Questions, comments, Kudo’s and yes, even some complaints, which we’ve used to continue to expand upon and update The Vertical Diet to help as many people as possible achieve their health and fitness goals. 
.
Victory Belt Publishing has done an outstanding job with the quality of this book and we’re excited to share it with you!!
.
Please be sure to let us know what you think. Thank you!!

node.text:
“Life Changing”
.
